| Feature | BitCrawl | Other Crawlers |
|---------|----------|----------------|
| **Easy to Use** | âœ… Simple Python API | âŒ Complex setup |
| **Smart Filtering** | âœ… Contextual content filtering | âŒ Raw data only |
| **Multiple Formats** | âœ… JSON, CSV, TXT output | âŒ Limited formats |
| **Flexible Crawling** | âœ… 5 different crawling modes | âŒ Single approach |
| **Developer Friendly** | âœ… Both CLI and Python API | âŒ API only |
| **Cost Efficient** | âœ… Reduces data volume by 70-90% | âŒ Full data extraction |

## ğŸ› ï¸ Key Features

- **ğŸ¯ Smart Content Filtering**: Reduce noise and extract only relevant content
- **ğŸ“Š Multiple Output Formats**: JSON, CSV, TXT for different use cases
- **ğŸ”„ Flexible Crawling Modes**: Scrape, crawl, search, map, extract
- **ğŸ“¦ Advanced Processing**: Automatic chunking and text processing
